#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"A free, personalized, integrated<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\"> "
"Website </font></strong>in a few clicks. Get new leads or direct appointment"
" online in a few clicks."
msgstr ""
"En gratis, personlig og integreret <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">"
"hjemmeside </font></strong> med blot et par klik. Få nye leads med blot et "
"par klik, eller aftal en tid direkte online."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid "Add an upfront payment in your Appointment Type."
msgstr "Føj en forudbetaling til din aftaletype."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Add the Subscription App and invoice automatically based on a subscription "
"type."
msgstr ""
"Tilføj Abonnementerappen, og udsted automatisk en faktura baseret på en "
"abonnementstype."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"After each appointment, an automatic email will be sent to suggest your "
"patient to already book its next appointment."
msgstr ""
"Efter hver konsultation sendes der automatisk en e-mail, hvor du foreslår "
"din patient at booke den næste konsultation allerede nu."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"As you qualify Emily's needs, you update the lead status to \"Qualified\" in"
" the CRM pipeline."
msgstr ""
"Så snart du har analyseret Emilys behov, skal du opdatere leadstatus i CRM-"
"pipeline til \"Kvalificeret\"."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid "Auto-post your invoice on a regular basis."
msgstr "Udsted din faktura regelmæssigt og automatisk."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Automated recurring invoicing with the <strong><font class=\"text-o-"
"color-1\">Subscription App</font></strong>."
msgstr ""
"Automatisér tilbagevendende fakturering med <strong><font class=\"text-o-"
"color-1\">Abonnementerappen</font></strong>."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid "Basics"
msgstr "Det grundlæggende"

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Be careful, using the \"Log Note\" in your contact with be displayed only "
"for you and your eventual team. If you select the \"Send message\" option, "
"this will notify your customer (which can be really interesting also)."
msgstr ""
"Vær opmærksom på, at funktionen \"Læg en besked\" kun vises for dig og dit "
"team på kontakten. Hvis du vælger \"Send besked\", modtager kunden en besked "
"(hvilket også kan være nyttigt)."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model:mail.template,name:wellness_practitioner.booking_suggestion
msgid "Book your next appointment"
msgstr "Book din næste aftale"

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"By installing this package, you'll have access to a range of essential apps,"
" including CRM, Appointment and Invoicing. Let's explore how these modules "
"can streamline your therapy practice operations."
msgstr ""
"Når du installerer denne pakke, får du adgang til en række vigtige apps, "
"herunder CRM, kalender og fakturering. Lad os se nærmere på, hvordan disse "
"moduler kan optimere din terapipraksis."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"By uploading this module's demo data, your database has been filled with a "
"few contacts."
msgstr "Når du uploader dette moduls demodata, tilføjes kontakter din database."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid "Discover more about Odoo by diving into our"
msgstr "Få mere at vide om Odoo i vores"

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid "Do you want to go further?"
msgstr "Vil du tage det et skridt videre?"

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Ease your invoicing process with the <strong><font class=\"text-o-"
"color-1\">Invoice App</font></strong>."
msgstr ""
"Forenkl din faktureringsproces med <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">"
"Faktureringsappen</font></strong>."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model:calendar.alarm,name:wellness_practitioner.alarm_mail_1
msgid "Follow up"
msgstr "Send rykker"

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Getting Started\n"
"            To begin, you'll find the key applications you need on your Odoo dashboard. Let's take a closer look at how you can use these tools."
msgstr ""
"Kom godt i gang\n"
"            På dit Odoo-dashboard finder du de vigtigste apps. Her viser vi, "
"hvordan du bedst bruger dem."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you navigate to the Invoice App, you can manage your invoices. You have "
"many possibilities to streamline your invoicing process:"
msgstr ""
"Når du går ind i Faktureringsappen, kan du administrere dine fakturaer. Der "
"er mange muligheder for at optimere din faktureringsproces:"

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you open Emily's opportunity in your CRM, you can see in the Chatter (on "
"the right column) that she received an email from you with a call to action "
"to book an appointment."
msgstr ""
"Når du åbner Emilys salgsmulighed i dit CRM-system, kan du i chatteren (i "
"højre kolonne) se, at hun har modtaget en e-mail fra dig, hvor du beder "
"hende om at aftale et møde."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you want to adapt your flow and set new automation rules, click the Gear "
"Icon in the top of a CRM column and select \"Automation\", or add automated "
"email in your Appointment Type."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du vil tilpasse din proces og oprette nye automatiseringsregler, skal "
"du klikke på tandhjulsikonet øverst i en CRM-kolonne og vælge "
"\"Automatisering\" eller tilføje en automatiseret e-mail i din aftaletype."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you want to share your calendar easily, navigate to the Appointment App "
"and select \"Share\" on the Edit Button."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du blot vil dele din kalender, skal du gå til appen \"Arrangementer\" "
"og klikke på \"Del\" på knappen \"Redigér\"."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"In the <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">CRM App</font></strong>, you "
"create a new lead for Emily, capturing her contact information and the "
"reason for her inquiry."
msgstr ""
"I <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">CRM-appen</font></strong> opretter "
"du et nyt lead for Emily og indtaster hendes kontaktoplysninger samt årsagen "
"til hendes henvendelse."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model:crm.stage,name:wellness_practitioner.crm_stage_5
msgid "Inactive"
msgstr "Inaktiv"

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid "Invoice yourself, manually."
msgstr "Udsted fakturaen til dig selv manuelt."

