msgstr "Jeg glæder mig til at møde dig"

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage all your communication channels in one place with Odoo<strong><font "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\"> Marketing Automation "
"</font></strong>,<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Email "
"Marketing</font></strong>,<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\"> Social "
"Media Marketing </font></strong>, and <strong><font class=\"text-o-"
"color-1\">SMS Marketing </font></strong>."
msgstr ""
"Styr alle dine kommunikationskanaler på ét sted med Odoo<strong><font "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\"> Automatiseret marketing </font></strong>,<strong>"
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\">E-mailmarketing</font></strong>,<strong><font "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\"> Markedsføring på sociale medier </font></strong> "
"og <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">SMS-marketing </font></strong>."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage your accounting easier than ever with a completely integrated "
"environment. (<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Accounting "
"App</font></strong>)"
msgstr ""
"Administrér din bogføring nemmere end nogensinde før i et fuldt integreret "
"miljø. (<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Regnskabsappen</font></"
"strong>)"

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage your team's and integrate them in all processes by adding "
"the<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\"> Employees App</font></strong>."
msgstr ""
"Administrér dit team og integrér det i alle processer ved at tilføje <strong>"
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Medarbejderappen</font></strong>."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid "Odoo for Therapy Practices"
msgstr "Odoo til terapipraksisser"

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Odoo is entirely integrated into an App. Download it to turn your phone to "
"manage your entire business in it."
msgstr ""
"Odoo er fuldt integreret i én app. Download den, og forvandl din telefon til "
"et værktøj, der administrerer hele din virksomhed."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid "Odoo offers you infinite possibilities, such as :"
msgstr "Odoo giver dig ubegrænsede muligheder, såsom:"

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Of course, this is just an overview of the features included in this "
"package. Feel free to add new apps, delete/modify demo data, and test "
"everything around!"
msgstr ""
"Oversigten viser naturligvis kun de funktioner, der følger med pakken. Du "
"kan tilføje nye apps, redigere eller slette demodata og prøve dig frem!"

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once the appointment is booked, navigate to the <strong><font class=\"text-"
"o-color-1\">Calendar App</font></strong>. You may find the new appointment. "
"You can also move it (Emily will be notified) or cancel it."
msgstr ""
"Så snart aftalen er booket, skal du gå til <strong><font class=\"text-o-"
"color-1\">Kalenderappen</font></strong>. Her kan du finde den nye aftale. Du "
"kan også flytte (Emily får besked) eller aflyse den."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Organise your events and connect with your patients easily with the "
"<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Events App </font></strong>."
msgstr ""
"Arrangér dine begivenheder, og hold kontakten med dine patienter via "
"<strong> <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Arrangementerappen </font></strong>."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model:crm.stage,name:wellness_practitioner.crm_stage_6
msgid "Redirect to Another Practitioner"
msgstr "Omdirigér til en anden behandler"

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid "Schedule a demo"
msgstr "Planlæg en demo"

